OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1775736665
OL,3,CWife of late footballer Joe Thompson
OL,4,Cpregnant from a frozen embryo
OL,6,FJoe Thompson's family Chantelle, Lula
OL,7,Fand Athena are preparing to mark the
OL,8,Fone year anniversary of his death from
OL,9,Fcancer. Granada Reports Sports
OL,10,FCorrespondent Mike Hall spoke to the
OL,11,Ffamily exclusively.
OL,13,FThe family of footballing hero Joe
OL,14,FThompson are continuing his legacy
OL,15,Fafter his wife Chantelle revealed she
OL,16,Fis pregnant with his baby after IVF
OL,17,Ftreatment using frozen embryos.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
