PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1775736665
OL,3,CWife of late footballer Joe Thompson
OL,4,Cpregnant from a frozen embryo
OL,6,FJoe Thompson died in 2025 after
OL,7,Fdeveloping cancer for a third time -
OL,8,Fbeating the illness twice to return to
OL,9,Fthe pitch and famously scoring a goal
OL,10,Fthat saved Rochdale FC from relegation
OL,11,Fin 2018.
OL,13,FBut when the former Manchester United,
OL,14,FTranmere Rovers and Rochdale star was
OL,15,Fdiagnosed with Hodgkin Lymphoma for a
OL,16,Fthird time, which had spread to his
OL,17,Flungs, he turned to fundraising,
OL,18,Fbefore he died aged 36.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1775736665
OL,3,CWife of late footballer Joe Thompson
OL,4,Cpregnant from a frozen embryo
OL,6,F"It just means absolutely everything.
OL,7,FI know it's never going to replace Joe
OL,8,Fobviously. Joe's Joe. But to be able
OL,9,Fto bring his baby into the world again
OL,10,Fis beautiful," Chantelle said.
OL,12,FShe said Joe had two visions of their
OL,13,Ffamily with a baby boy before he died.
OL,15,F"He actually had a vision of us sat
OL,16,Foutside with a baby boy. This was
OL,17,Fmaybe six months before he passed, and
OL,18,Fhe assumed that it was all of us.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1775736665
OL,3,CWife of late footballer Joe Thompson
OL,4,Cpregnant from a frozen embryo
OL,6,F"And then maybe two weeks before he
OL,7,Fpassed, we were just sat in the garden
OL,8,Fand he just had a realisation and was
OL,9,Flike, 'I think I was watching you with
OL,10,Fthe baby and the girls in the garden,
OL,11,Fnot me physically here with you',"
OL,12,FChantelle added.
OL,14,FJoe even gave her the name for the
OL,15,Fbaby boy he predicted, and she got
OL,16,Fpregnant on her first attempt of IVF
OL,17,Fafter he had died.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1775736665
OL,3,CWife of late footballer Joe Thompson
OL,4,Cpregnant from a frozen embryo
OL,6,FBut, the mum-to-be does not yet know
OL,7,Fthe gender of their baby, and has an
OL,8,Femail with the answer sitting unopened
OL,9,Fon her computer.
OL,11,FShe will join her and Joe's families
OL,12,Fin a small gathering to find out if he
OL,13,Fwas right. "I hope so because I've
OL,14,Fonly got a boy's name," said Chantelle.
OL,16,FChantelle is 25 weeks pregnant, and
OL,17,Fsays she was sat with her daughters in
OL,18,FBali when she found out she would be
OL,19,Fhaving another baby.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1775736665
OL,3,CWife of late footballer Joe Thompson
OL,4,Cpregnant from a frozen embryo
OL,6,FTheir daughter Lula said: "When it had
OL,7,Ftwo lines I was in shock, my brain
OL,8,Fwent completely blank.
OL,10,F"I was happy but I was just so
OL,11,Fsurprised."
OL,13,FJoe and Chantelle had lost their baby
OL,14,FDre who sadly died just three days
OL,15,Fbefore he was due.
OL,17,FChantelle spoke about Dre as she said:
OL,18,F"It means absolutely everything, and
OL,19,Fto be blessed for it to work first
OL,20,Ftime.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1775736665
OL,3,CWife of late footballer Joe Thompson
OL,4,Cpregnant from a frozen embryo
OL,6,F"We'd gone through IVF for three years
OL,7,Ftrying to get pregnant with baby Dre.
OL,9,F"But I just knew, I knew the timing
OL,10,Fwas right, I knew Joe's messages were
OL,11,Fright."
OL,13,FBefore they welcome the new arrival,
OL,14,Fthere will be another celebration of
OL,15,FJoe's life.
OL,17,FOn 2 May, friends and fans will repeat
OL,18,Fhis 2024 fundraising walk - starting
OL,19,Fat Rochdale and ending at Manchester
OL,20,FUnited.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1775736665
OL,3,CWife of late footballer Joe Thompson
OL,4,Cpregnant from a frozen embryo
OL,6,F"It's just something we want to do
OL,7,Fannually, just to celebrate Joe and
OL,8,Fremember Joe, because life does go on
OL,9,Ffor everyone else as well, and I think
OL,10,Ffor us it's important that we can
OL,11,Fcontinue the work he did when he was
OL,12,Fhere, and keep that alive," said
OL,13,FChantelle.
OL,15,FIt will be one year on from Joe's
OL,16,Fdeath on 17 April, and Chantelle say
OL,17,Fshe is feeling apprehensive ahead of
OL,18,Fthe day.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1775736665
OL,3,CWife of late footballer Joe Thompson
OL,4,Cpregnant from a frozen embryo
OL,6,FShe said: "I try to see the positive
OL,7,Fin things. Don't get me wrong, there
OL,8,Fis times where I do think 'Why us? Why
OL,9,Fhave the girls not their dad? Why have
OL,10,Fwe gone through this?'
OL,12,F"...You've got to also allow yourself
OL,13,Fto be sad, but then also try and think
OL,14,Fof the positives, and what a guy he
OL,15,Fwas, and all the memories that we had
OL,16,Ftogether, and the 13 years I've had
OL,17,Fwith him."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
